



Sir,
Fredericksburgh April 22d 1758



I am this moment arrived, and find your orders to march, which shall be Complyd with; tho The President gave directions for refreshing the men and Paying them off here1As soon as the men are on their March I will come on, and hope the pleasure of Seeing you thursday night;2 in the mean time; I am with Respect, Sir, your most Obt Hube Sert

Adam Stephen

